Well - marbles of course. Rnd - oh well - when we were - when were youngsters like that we used to play - well with tennis racquets you know and just - that - not actually good - right tennis but - 
we could - bat it, the ball to each other and - and - catcher of course and - played away that way. And - if we got a football which was very seldom - we had plenty of room to play - kick a ball about. Aye.
