Yes, on wet days we used to be invited across - to - a family name of Downie and they had - a nursery further along nearer - Halgreen Road, and they have a shop in - Chadwick Place yet, that\rquote s the same firm but - all the family are dead 
but then that - name\rquote 
s kept up. And - there was two girls and a boy there that we had - my sister and I was invited over on wet days to play in the - the day nursery. And - we had - pretty nice fun and different games there, games that you bought you know 
- sorts of puzzles of different kinds you know and - fill in - the time that way.
