\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Your homework took up most of the time did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Did you ever go fishing, you went fishing for minnows?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Did you go for walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 
Yes, we went a walk - with my father usually, just a short walk - on a Sunday afternoon in between the churches you see, in between - the morning church and the evening church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Did you have a bicycle when you were a child?
