inburgh team - once I was - up a bit and - I would be about - seventeen or eighteen, I was playing for - an Edinburgh club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Did you ever go to the theatre or concerts or music halls?
