\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Oh yes, away from - in 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7162943\charrsid1324535 Yet}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 
 until the end of 1918 from when you were a child. Would you say there were different social classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 1918 girl I was in the Army. Why - well - I was - a married man by that time with two a family, in 1918.
