\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Oh there was different classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 And what would you call them at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Well there was the workers, there was the - people that was better off and they didna need to work you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 What sort of class would they be called?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Oh well, the middle class maybe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 So that was the working class and the middle class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 
Aye. The like of the - the Downies now - they had that big nursery you see and - there was a mother and father and - two girls - and a son, and they had two maids, well - we considered them - better off than - than real
ly the middle class because they - they didna need to work and they seemed to be always - v}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7162943\charrsid1324535 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 
ry flush and they went away for a month\rquote s holidays in the summer and - different story.
