\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Oh the working class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 What other sort of people belonged to the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Well - all tr}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7162943\charrsid1324535 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 desmen and - labourers and - whatnot, they were all working class, they had to work to live.
