\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 We went to - a place outside Kidderminster, to another brother - of the - my wife\rquote s. Blace called - it
 was Broom Cottage anyway but I - outside Kidderminster it is.
