\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 But did your wife have a job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Oh no. Well - she - yes, she was in a coal office - for a - time.
