\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Oh aye, I did - I did help. Yes.
