\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 And feed them and play with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Aye.
