\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Oh yes - after I started business I - did a lot of work for them. \lquote 
Cos - they stayed along at - Downie Terrace, or St. Catherine's Gardens really, and - it was a Mr Youngers, he built the lower - in fact he built Victor Park Terrace and Maybank Villas, and - after I started business of course I got a lot of work from h
im.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7680140 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 Was he a good kind of landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10179441 WS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2764154\charrsid1324535 
